title: Google Pixel 7a - Unlocked Android Cell Phone - Smartphone with Wide Angle Lens and 24-Hour Battery - 128 GB – Charcoal
description: Meet Pixel 7a, engineered by Google. It’s powered by the Google Tensor G2 chip, so it’s super fast and secure, and designed for extra online protection with VPN by Google One.[1,11] The Pixel Camera takes amazing photos and videos, and even helps you breathe life into old pictures with its advanced features. And the battery lasts all day.[2] All for less than you think.
features: Fast Charging: Pixel 7a has a 24-hour battery life and supports fast charging up to 72 hours with Extreme Battery Saver turned on.
Advanced Camera: Pixel 7a has a 6.1-inch OLED display with 1080p video capture and a 64MP rear camera that performs well in low light.

Security Features: Pixel 7a has a 6.1-inch OLED display with 1080p video capture and a 64MP rear camera that performs well in low light. It also has a biometric fingerprint sensor for quick unlocking.
Wireless Connectivity: Pixel 7a supports NFC, Wi-Fi, USB, and Bluetooth for easy connectivity to other devices.
Water Resistant Design: Pixel 7a has a water-resistant design that allows you to use it even in rainy or wet conditions.
Long Battery Life: Pixel 7a has a 4385mAh battery that provides up to 24 hours of use per charge, with the option to extend battery life up to 72 hours with Extreme Battery Saver.
Dual SIM Card Slots: Pixel 7a has dual SIM card slots for convenient use with two separate phone numbers.
Google Tensor G2 Processor: Pixel 7a is powered by a Google Tensor G2 processor for fast performance and advanced AI features.
Google Assistant Integration: Pixel 7a has Google Assistant integration for hands-free assistance and control.
1 Year Manufacturer Warranty: Pixel 7a comes with a 1 year manufacturer warranty for peace of mind and protection.

description: Meet the all-new motorola razr with a super stylish, pocket-friendly flip design. Available in a range of fun, trendsetting colors and a vegan leather finish, motorola razr reimagines what a phone can do. Discover new ways to interact, capture, and create by folding your phone so it stands on its own at multiple angles. Go all day and night on a single charge of its outstanding battery. View notifications on an external display with the phone closed, so you’re always up to date. Then flip it open to reveal an ultra-smooth, incredibly vivid 6.9" pOLED screen combined with multidimensional sound for immersive entertainment. Add to that its 64MP and 32MP high-res cameras, and you’ve got a phone like no other. Embrace the unexpected with the new motorola razr.
features: Compatible with T-Mobile 5G and Verizon a5G. Ready for 5G on other select networks dependent on availability; contact your service provider for details. Compatible with all major 4G U.S. carriers, including Verizon, ATandT, and T-Mobile. It also works with prepaid carriers, including Cricket Wireless, Metro by T-Mobile, Simple Mobile, Total Wireless, Tracfone, Net10, Mint, TracFone, and H2O.
Iconic foldable design. Flip the script with a pocket-friendly flip design in a range of fun, trendsetting colors and a vegan leather finish.
Capture like never before. With Flex View, stand your phone on its own at multiple angles, giving you entirely new ways to interact, capture, and create.
All-day battery life. Go a full day and night on a single charge of the 4200mAh battery, fuel up fast with TurboPowe 30W charging, or charge wirelessly.
All your essentials at a glance. View notifications, check the weather, snap a selfie, and more, all without having to flip open your phone.
Immersive entertainment. Flip open the phone to reveal an ultra-smooth, incredibly vivid 6.9" pOLED screen, combined with Dolby Atmos and Spatial Sound.
Versatile high-res cameras. Snap brilliant photos and selfies in any light with a 64MP external camera and OIS—or a 32MP internal camera with Quad Pixel technology.
Powerful Snapdragon 7 Gen 1 processor. Fuel next-generation gaming, entertainment, and connectivity, including big screen Ready For experiences.

title: 73"-Phone-Tripod-with-Horizontal-Overhead, Selfie Stick/Tall Travel Tripod Stand with Wireless Remote and iPhone Holder, Mirrorless/Compact/GoPro Camera Tripod Compatible iPhone/Smartphone
breadCrumbs: Cell Phones & Accessories › Accessories › Photo & Video Accessories › Photo & Video Kits
features: KEY FEATURES - 1.Lightweight and Compat: This tall cell Phone tripod is made of lightweight aerospace aluminum alloy, weighing only 1.5 lbs. When folded, it measures just 16.5 inches, fitting easily into your backpack without adding extra weight. 2.Tall Enouth: When fully extended, the tripod can hold your phone at a height of 73 inches, fully meeting your everyday needs. 3.Horizontal Shooting: The center column can be extended and inserted into the horizontal conversion port, transforming it into an overhead shooting tripod. You can mount your phone 13.8 inches from the central axis of the tripod.

SIMPLE AND FLEXIBLE HEAD - This is a simple cell phone tripod with a 1/4-inch screw on the tripod head, allowing you to attach the included rotating phone holder, a compact camera, a mirrorless camera, or a GoPro. The tripod is very lightweight, making it ideal for filming, vlogging, live streaming, and video recording during outdoor travel. The tripod head has three joints, each controlling different functions: 360° horizontal rotation, 180° tilt adjustment, and switching between landscape and portrait modes for the phone.

VERY PRACTICAL FEATURES - 1. The phone tripod is manufactured using rapid cooling injection molding, featuring engineering plastic and aluminum alloy. Its components are precise, and the head rotates smoothly, providing an excellent user experience. 2. The tripod head includes 2 bubble levels to assist in keeping your phone in perfect horizontal and vertical shooting positions. 3. We provide you with a remote control, allowing convenient remote operation of your phone's camera shutter for easy selfies. 4. The center column can be used as a selfie stick, with a total length of 17.7 inches.

OFF-AXIS OVERHEAD SHOOTING FUNCTION - This lightweight cellphone tripod provides a stable shooting position at a height of 55 inches off the ground. When fully extended, you can extend your phone up to 17.7 inches away from the tripod's central axis while maintaining stability. From this shooting angle, you can freely capture various tabletop instructional videos such as cooking, painting, and crafts.

IMPORTANT REMINDER - This tripod was designed with certain trade-offs in mind, so please note the following: 1.This tripod is designed for phones, supporting up to 2.5 lbs, suitable for all phones, GoPros, compact cameras, and most mirrorless cameras. Please avoid using devices heavier than this limit. 2. When the tripod cannot fully extend in overhead shooting mode, the support surface may not stabilize the horizontal bar enough to prevent tipping. In such situations, if your phone is positioned at its maximum off-axis distance, you'll need to attach a counterweight to the opposite end of the horizontal bar to maintain balance.

BASIC PARAMETERS - Name: iPhone Tripod, Smartphone Tripod, Mirrorless Camera/Compact Camera Tripod. Compatible with all phones with a width of 1.96~3.3 inches; Tripod legs fully extended height: 73 inches; Tripod legs fully extended with center column retracted height: 60 inches; Height of phone in overhead mode: 60 inches; Minimum support height: 17.7 inches; Independent center column length (can be used as a selfie stick) : 17.7 inches; Tripod weight: 1.5 lbs

AFTER-SALES - Within two years, any quality issues with the product can be promptly replaced. We provide corresponding accessories to ensure that lost parts can be purchased during use. Simply search "CAMBOFOTO 205C" to find what you need.

From the manufacturer
A phone full of firsts. 
Meet Pixel 9 with Gemini. Engineered by Google, Pixel gets the best of Google AI first. So you can take amazing photos and get things done even easier. Pixel can protect against spam and other threats. It helps you in an emergency.[9] And it’s built to last. 
Previous page
Take the picture. And be in it, too. 
Add Me makes sure no one is left out. Take a photo with the group, then swap in the photographer.[2] 
Group pics the whole group loves. 
Best Take combines similar photos into one fantastic picture where everyone looks their best. 
Frame it perfectly with Magic Editor. 
It helps reframe your photo, crops it just right, and can even expand it to get more of the scene. 
Reimagine the scenery. 
With Magic Editor, turn grass into a beach or make the sky pink. Just type what you want to see.[2] 
Make stuff disappear. 
Erase photobombers, crowds, powerlines, or other distractions, just like that.

Water and scratch resistant 
Pixel can handle water, dust, and scratches with IP68 protection. And with Corning Gorilla Glass Victus 2.1, the display is scratch and damage resistant.[16]

Google Tensor G4 and RAM
Pixel 9 runs fast and smooth with 12 GB of RAM. And it’s designed to handle Google’s advanced AI.

title: REDMAGIC 9S Pro Smartphone 5G, 120Hz Gaming Phone, 6.8" Full Screen, Under Display Camera, 6500mAh Android Phone, Snapdragon 8 Gen 3, 12+256GB, 80W Charger, Dual-Sim, US Unlocked Cell Phone Black
features: 【6.8" FHD+ Full Screen】Gaming Phone with a 120Hz refresh rate and a resolution of 2480 x 1116 pixels, this 6.8" FHD+ Full AMOLED screen delivers beautiful HD+ visuals at up to 120 frames per second. With a 960Hz touch sampling rate for multi fingers, the Cell Phone delivers ultra-fast touch and precise response, giving you a serious competitive edge while gaming. The 5G Smartphone have also Under-display Fingerprint Sensor and 16MP Under Display Camera.

【Latest Chip and Larger Storage】The Gaming Smartphone has the latest Qualcomm Snapdragon 8 Gen 3 Leading Version(Red Core 2 Pro + UFS 4.0 + LPDDR5X). Play your favorite games with ease with the raw power of the new CPU clocking in at nearly 3.4GHz and enjoy Triple-A graphics thanks to the fast rendering power of the GPU. 12GB RAM + 256GB ROM provides not only a fun gaming experience and effects, also large storage space for game downloads.

【Multi-Dimensional Cooling System】The Gaming Phone incorporates new aerospace-grade phase change materials (PCM) . Heat can be stored inside this material and released slowly so you feel less heat from the phone while playing, making it more comfortable to hold the phone. The High-Speed Built-In Turbofan accelerates heat dissipation and the fan noise is as quiet as a whisper.

【5G & WIFI Connection and 80W fast charging】5G is SA+NSA dual mode and supports all key regions up to 3.0 Gbps uploads, up to 7.5 Gbps downloads. WIFI 7 is up to 3.5Gbps. These bring mobile gaming to a whole new level. Download the latest games and videos in gigabit speeds with ease to show off your smooth, low latency experience. The Cell Phone certified 80W GAN charger and supports 80W fast charging.

【Ultra HD AI Quad Camera】Rear Camera are Samsung GN5 50MP(Wide) + Samsung JN1 50MP(Ultrawide) + 2MP(Macro). The primary camera is upgraded to enable users to take fantastic photos and videos with a fast auto focus, even in the dimmest scenario. Every detail is captured. Thanks to dual pixel focusing, it ensures fast autofocus regardless. Front Camera is 16 Megapixel and 5nd generation under-display-camera (UDC).

title: 200W USB C Charger Block, GaN III 8-Port USB C Fast Charging Station PPS PD 65W Laptop Charger Adapter Compatible with MacBook Pro/Air,DELL,HP Surface,iPhone 16/15/Pro/14/13,Galaxy,Steam Deck-White
breadCrumbs: Cell Phones & Accessories › Accessories › Chargers & Power Adapters › Wall Chargers
features: 【8-in-1 USB C Charger】This usb c charger block provides 8 charging wattage options with 4 USB-C ports and 4 USB-A ports. Such a usb c multiport charger can handle all your devices at fast speed. What's cool is that you can charge laptop with top usb c ports of 65w and also compatible with PPS 45W fast charging.

【Latest GAN III Chip Technology】 The USB C charger adopted GaN III generation chip technology, built-in multi-protection system and premium microchips. With higher energy efficiency, higher resistance to radiation and upgraded heat dissipation, Gallium Nitride (GaN) makes our chargers smaller and safer without sacrificing a drop of power. Built-in overcharge protection, overheating protection, short circuit protection, over-current protection, over-voltage protection.

【USB C GaN Charger Universal Compatibility】Charge virtually all your mobile and tablet Laptop devices at maximum speed with USB-C and standard USB A input. Say goodbye to tangled cables and messy clutter. 65w port can act as a usb c laptop charger to power your laptops, Compatible with MacBook Pro MacBook Air Dell XPS all iPhone airpods Steam Deck and more

【Fast Charging GaN Charger】Usb c charging station deliver the optimal power output to charge different device at full speed. It is possible to quickly charge your laptop and iPhone at the same time. Charging MacBook Pro 14” to 38% in half an hour, charging iPhone to 50% in half an hour, The GaN chipset increases the charging efficiency up to 90%.

【Portable USB C Charging Station】USB C charger using first-class ABS+PC material will not easily heat up like aluminum alloy shell, color-block design to increase the sense of premium. Small size ensure maximum portability wherever you go. come with a 59inch/1.5m detachable power cord so even you plug in multiple devices it can stand on the desktop, dresser and nightstand. No more hunting for outlets or lugging around a bunch of chargers when travel, much simplify your life.
【What You Get】1 x USB C Charger, 1 x Power cord, 1 x Instructions, 90-day money back guarantee, industry-leading 3-year warranty, and lifetime technical support.

title: nubia Z70 Ultra 5g Android Cellphone - Snapdragon 8 Elite Smartphone with Triple Cameras, UDC Tech, Unlocked Phone with 144Hz 6.85" AMOLED Screen, 6150mAh, 80W Fast Charging, IP68&IP69 Waterproof
features: 【Expansive Full Screen】Discover a stunning 6.85-inch AMOLED display that boasts a 144Hz refresh rate and peaks at a dazzling 2,000 nits, providing users with crystal-clear visuals and vibrant colors. Meanwhile, designed with an ultra-thin bezel, this display features an innovative UDC (Under Display Camera) for an uninterrupted, immersive view. Experience an ultra-responsive performance whether you’re gaming, streaming, or multitasking—no distractions, just pure visual power.

【Capture Your Vision】The nubia Z70 Ultra cellphone is the world’s first smartphone camera equipped with a 35mm Adjustable Physical Aperture. Featuring a 50MP main camera with a variable aperture, a 64MP periscope lens for zooming in, and a 50MP ultrawide lens for those epic group shots, this 5g smartphone enables you to snag the perfect shot every time, whether it's a breathtaking landscape or a candid moment.

【Pristine Power Unleashed】Fueled by the cutting-edge Snapdragon 8 Elite chip, nubia Z70 Ultra Android phone allows you to multitask effortlessly and browse at lightning speeds. Made out of silicon carbon anode, this powerhouse of a battery promises uninterrupted use with a robust 6150mAh. When it’s time to recharge, 80W fast charging gets you back up to speed instantly. Whether you're streaming videos or gaming on the go, the battery capacity ensures there are no limits.

【Meet Nebula AIOS】Effortlessly Intuitive, meet Nebula AIOS—the intelligent system that adapts to you. Built to streamline your day, its intuitive features simplify tasks and boost productivity. With a user-friendly design, this AI-power system keeps you one step ahead. Explore the funny AI functions, including Voice Assistant, AI Gallery Search, AI Translate, AI Portrait Highlights, a Bokeh effect for photos, and more.

【Tackle Any Adventure】This 1.3 mm edges slim, elegant, and stunningly crafted nubia Z70 Ultra unlocked cellphone is equipped with an IP68 rating and an improved IP69 rating. Completely water and dust-proof, it is resistant to high temperatures and high-pressure water. Rain or shine, enjoy your day thanks to a robust build and carefully crafted exterior.

【Unlocked For All Carriers】Please Confirm Your SIM Card's frequency bands are included in the below-supported Bands before Ordering. NSA: n41/n77/n78(3.3~3.6GHz)/n38; SA: n41/n77/n78(3.3~3.6GHz)/n1/n3/n5/n8/n28/n2/n7/n40/n66/n38/n25/n20/n26; FDD: B1/2/3/4/5/7/8/12/17/18/19/20/25/26/28/66; TDD: B34/39/40/41/38/42; UMTS: B1/2/4/5/6/8/19; GSM: B2/3/5/8.

title: Xiaomi Redmi 13 (24049RN28L), 256GB 8GB RAM, Dual SIM, Factory Unlocked GSM, International Version - (Midnight Black)
description: The Redmi 13 is an impressive entry-level smartphone featuring a large 6.79-inch IPS LCD display with a 90Hz refresh rate, providing smooth visuals and a crisp 1080 x 2460 pixel resolution. It stands out with a 108MP main camera, offering exceptional photo quality in its price range. Powered by the Mediatek Helio G91 Ultra chipset, it ensures decent performance for everyday tasks. The phone boasts a robust 5030mAh battery with 33W fast charging, supporting long usage times and quick recharges. Additional features include dual SIM support, microSD expandable storage, and a side-mounted fingerprint sensor for secure access. The design is sleek, available in various appealing colors, and includes practical extras like a 3.5mm audio jack and IR blaster. Despite its budget nature, it has a solid build with Gorilla Glass protection and basic IP53 water resistance. Overall, the Redmi 13 balances affordability with impressive features, making it a strong contender in the budget smartphone market.

ANDROID 14, 365-DAY U.S. WARRANTY and HOTLINE SUPPORT - Experience the pure performance of stock Android 14, free from bloatware and ads. Is expandable storage compatible with phone? 
Yes, the NUU N10 supports expandable storage via microSD card up to 128GB (sold separately). However, when using a microSD card for expansion, only one Nano SIM card can be used. 
Does it allow simultaneous use of two SIM cards? 
Yes, it supports two SIM cards in standby mode, perfect for managing personal and work numbers. 
Are camera features good for low light? 
The camera works well in good lighting conditions. For better low-light photos, try using the built-in flash and night mode 
Is phone compatible with popular streaming apps and services? 
Yes, with Android 14, this phone is perfect for all your favourite streaming apps and services 
After the 30-day return period, if my device has issues, do you offer any type of support? 
For over 10 years, we’ve supported all customers. Our Texas team is ready to help anytime. We offer 365 days of support for repairs or replacements due to manufacturing defects. Reach out to us for more details!

title: Gimbal Stabilizer for Smartphone ，with Retractable Selfie Stick and Tripod，1-Axis Multifunction Remote 360°Automatic Rotation， Auto Balance for iPhone/Android
breadCrumbs: Cell Phones & Accessories › Accessories › Photo & Video Accessories › Handheld Gimbals & Stabilizers
features: Superior Image Stabilization：With its powerful sports gyroscope, 1-Axis gimbal stabilizer can be a perfect companion for capturing smooth and stable footage by eliminating hand shaking during filming. Good choice for VLOG, Live Video, Youtube, Tiktok, live streaming, action camera.

Easy and Intuitive Operation: No need APP! Designed with user-friendliness in mind, Fisherfans gimbal offers an easy-to-use controls. You can easily change the clip head to be horizontal and vertical with a simple press, saving you from tedious manual adjustments.

Portable Selfie Stick: Weighs only 0.49lb and measures 7.5 inches when folded. 31.5 inches extendable aluminum alloy rod gives you the perfect length for capturing shots. The flexible phone holder rotates 270°, allowing you to find the best angle for your selfies and group photos.

Stable Tripod: Transforming the gimbal into a stable phone tripod by simply opening the hand grip and placing it on any flat surface. The thicken rod can be adjusted to the ideal height for watching/shooting videos, video chatting , taking selfies, or capturing group photos. Enjoying hands-free stability for your needs.

Wide Compatibility: The extendable phone clip head is compatible with most smartphones within the range of 4.0-6.2 inches. It can also be adapted to work with GoPro cameras by changing the base to a 1/4 connector, providing wider compatibility options for your creative endeavors.

aPlusContent.title: Product Description
aPlusContent.rawText:
Product Description
The 1-Axis GIMBAL STABILIZER FOR SMARTPHONE is born for filming your live. Everyone can direct his/her own interesting VLOG. 
This junior Single-Axis Gimbal Stabilizer for smartphone is suitable for novices,We don't recommend use it as a professional stabilizer. 
Grip the gimbal, go out to record & share what you saw & how you feel about this world, without hesitation & fuzzy.Everyone can be a director easily. 
Do you have the following troubles: 
1. You want to professionally shoot the scenery and the wide range of changes over a long period of time, but there is no professional equipment or the equipment is too heavy to carry. 
2. You want to shoot yourself a VLOG, but you haven't found a small professional device which is easy to operate, automatically follow you, and record your life naturally and smoothly. 
Get a gimbal stabilizer, your troubles will no longer exist. 
· None of shake - No matter how rough the road you are walking, no matter how fast of your speed, just keep you video stable and record every moment without missing. Your life is so wonderful that should no 
Premium aluminum alloy stick make the tripod more stable, convenient to long distance snapshot or recording video for party, travel and video chat 
Tpey-c port charging 
The gimbal is auto balanced to prevent device shaking and image blur. No matter how your angle and position change, it will always stay stable and the camera will focus on one point. 
Thanks to the gimbal stabilizer upside-down detection and rotation technology, the smartphone gimbal stabilizer can rotate your phone You can shoot with your phone even at the extremely low angle such as beneath the subject and look straight up at it. 
gimbal stabilizer is only 0.47lb and 7.5 inches for folded size. The lightweight and compact design, easy to pack in your bag or even in your pocket. 
Removable clip head allows this gimbal compatible with gopro if you have the connector.(The connector not included) 
With removable wireless remote control, control distance up to 32ft, excellent for snapping selfies or group photos from afar. 
First of all, you need to know the function of the buttons on the device. 
There is a Mode Change Button behind the clip head and a Intelligent Button beside the clip head. 
Gimbal Mode: 
When you need to use the Gimbal mode, you need to unlock the mode change button first.
And long press the intelligent button, when the light turns green, the Gimbal Mode is active.
And then you just need to short press the intelligent button to change the position you want.
Selfie Stick Mode: 
When you need to use the Selfie Stick Mode, you need to make sure that the Gimbal Mode is off.
If the light is green, you need to long press the intelligent button to turn off the Gimabl Mode. If the light is dark, it means the Gimbal Mode is already off.
And then put the clip head to the position you want and lock the mode change button to fix the position.
